						<div class="postbody">- The test <em>vbl_clear_time.nes</em> (from the package <em>blargg_ppu_tests.zip</em>) gives me error $02 (VBL flag cleared too soon). On other side, another test <em>4.vbl_clear_timing.nes</em> (from the package <em>vbl_nmi_timing.zip</em>) doesn't give me an error (passed). However, if I fix the vbl_clear_time by delaying 1 ppu cycle, the other (4.vbl_clear_timing.nes) gives me error 7 (Flag should read as set 2 PPU clocks after VBL).
<br />
<br />- I need some help.</div>

					
