				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I already explained this thing. Here's an example:
<br />
<br />- If ppu_cycles_left=0 and ppu_cycle=341, then the VBlank flag is set <strong>and</strong> 2002h reads 80h.
<br />
<br />- If ppu_cycles_left=3 and ppu_cycle=0, then the VBlank flag is set <strong>and</strong> 2002h <em>did</em> read 00h.
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">;defaults<br />NOP<br />;-vblank set-<br />BIT $2002<br /><br />;case 1<br />NOP<br />BIT $2002 <br />;24 02 20|ppu_cycle_341, VBlank set<br />;&#40;reads 80h&#41;<br /><br />;case 2<br />NOP<br />BIT $2002<br />;24 02 20|ppu_cycle_341<br />LDA #$01<br />;ppu_cycle_0|A9 01<br />;VBlank set, but never read.</div></div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><strong>Zepper</strong><br /><a href="http://rocknes.web.fc2.com/" class="postlink"><em>RockNES developer</em></a></div>
